  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Drought Nutrition Support</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The main objective of this UNICEF project is to provide nutrition support for individuals affected by the drought. UNICEF will provide treatment for 2812 severely malnourished children through the procurement and distribution of nutrition supplements in health facilities. UNICEF will also ensure that the 4 priority districts have skilled IYCF counsellors in the health facilities together with nutritional screening and awareness raising. Some 132,146 drought affected individuals will be reached over 6 months.</narrative>
  </description>
